Fogos.pt (https://fogos.pt) created and proved the model of open,
community-driven wildfire information in Portugal. FogosPortugal exists
because of that work and gratefully credits it.

Data displayed by this product comes from ANEPC / Proteção Civil, ICNF,
IPMA, NASA FIRMS, RainViewer, Open-Meteo, and CARTO / OpenStreetMap
contributors. Attribution requirements of those sources apply to reuse of
their data.
